On today’s show, Emily is joined by Australian sex influencer, Nadia Bokody, to chat about taking control of your sexuality and be proud.

They discuss how to own your sexuality and what it truly means to be a f*ckgirl. Plus, what to do if your partner is invited to their ex’s wedding and ways to get your partner’s head into the oral game.
